== 創作 ==
小說家丹尼爾·韓德勒以[[筆名|筆名]]「雷蒙尼·史尼奇」出版了這部系列小說<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.express.co.uk/showbiz/tv-radio/753864/Netflix-who-is-Daniel-Handler-who-plays-Lemony-Snicket-in-A-Series-of-Unfortunate-Events|title=Who is Daniel Handler? Who plays Lemony Snicket in A Series of Unfortunate Events?|last=Foster|first=Alice|date=2017-01-13|newspaper=Express.co.uk|accessdate=2018-09-04|language=en|archive-date=2019-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191030004634/https://www.express.co.uk/showbiz/tv-radio/753864/Netflix-who-is-Daniel-Handler-who-plays-Lemony-Snicket-in-A-Series-of-Unfortunate-Events|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由於韓德勒喜歡詩人[[夏爾·波特萊爾|夏爾·波特萊爾]]的作品的緣故，所以才將《波特萊爾大遇險》故事主角的姓設定為「波特萊爾」。他也表示故事中波特萊爾三姐弟的悲慘遭遇在某種程度上類似現實中[[猶太人|猶太人]]的經歷<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.momentmag.com/jewish-secrets-lemony-snicket/|title=The Jewish Secrets of Lemony Snicket|author=|date=2017-01-13|newspaper=Moment Magazine|accessdate=2018-09-04|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112035858/https://momentmag.com/jewish-secrets-lemony-snicket/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

